# Security Scan - SAST agent

NAME sast-scanner

INPUT task

GOAL scan """
Perform static application security testing on the provided code.
Check for: injection flaws (SQL, command, XSS), auth issues,
cryptographic weaknesses, insecure deserialization, hardcoded secrets,
buffer overflows / memory safety.
Output findings in severity order (CRITICAL > HIGH > MEDIUM > LOW).
Include line references, CWE IDs, and remediation guidance.
""" -> vulnerabilities

RUN main USING scan
